State:
Abstract class
Particular state where a specific set of inputs will be taken into account

StateDropZone     Dropping a Unit from a Vehicle
StateGlobal       Try to treat not handled events (Chain of commands)
StateMenu         Generic menu
StateMenuCrew     Menu crew (allowing browsing left / right)
StateMovingUnit   Moving a Unit
StatePlaying      Active while browsing the map
StateSelectTarget Active while browsing the map


Stackables (StateGlobal is always active though (close the window, ...))
^ StateSelectTarget
| StateMenu
| StatePlaying
